# One scene, a whole wardrobe. The tape is the recording; the dress is
# post-production — VHS ignores the cue below and still records this
# tape, just undressed.

Output macos.gif
# foley: dress macos

Set Width 700
Set Height 340
Set FontSize 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "echo 'same tape, dressed as: macos'"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Type "seq 1 3"
Enter
Sleep 2s
